{"id": 6313, "title": "Ticket #6313: Allow tools to report on all annexes.", "description": "<blockquote>\nIn particular:\n\n<p></p><ol>\n<li>Running 'condor_status -annex' without an annex name should return all machines in any annex.  Could be implemented with a 'AnnexName is defined' constraint (do we care about backwards compatibility?), but do it with a dedicated flag for later user simplicity.\n\n<p></p></li><li>Likewise for 'condor_off -annex' without an annex name.\n\n<p></p></li><li><div class=\"strike\">\n<strike>Likewise for 'condor_annex -status'.</strike></div>\n  Turns out this isn't really going to work -- we don't know which <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClientTokens\" title=\"Client Tokens\">ClientTokens</a></span> embed annex names, and just reporting on everything with a <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=ClientToken\" title=\"Client Token\">ClientToken</a></span> will have all of the false negatives.\n\n<p></p></li><li>Implement <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=IsAnnex\" title=\"Is Annex\">IsAnnex</a></span> flag, adjust above constraints to use it.</li></ol>\n</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2017-Aug-16 19:26</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=52138\">[52138]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6313\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6313'); return false;\" title=\"Allow tools to report on all annexes.\">#6313</a></span>) Update wiki links in the manual.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2017-Aug-16 18:32</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=52137\">[52137]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6313\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6313'); return false;\" title=\"Allow tools to report on all annexes.\">#6313</a></span>) Fix bad usage information for -annex-slots.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2017-Jun-27 17:39</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=51812\">[51812]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6313\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6313'); return false;\" title=\"Allow tools to report on all annexes.\">#6313</a></span>) Add <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=IsAnnex\" title=\"Is Annex\">IsAnnex</a></span> flag, convert -annex (w/o name) to use.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2017-Jun-22 15:30</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=51801\">[51801]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6313\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6313'); return false;\" title=\"Allow tools to report on all annexes.\">#6313</a></span>) condor_off -annex fixes.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2017-Jun-22 15:11</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=51799\">[51799]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6313\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6313'); return false;\" title=\"Allow tools to report on all annexes.\">#6313</a></span>) Added -annex[-name] [&lt;name&gt;] to condor_off.  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2017-Jun-22 10:49</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=51794\">[51794]</a></span>: (<span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=6313\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('6313'); return false;\" title=\"Allow tools to report on all annexes.\">#6313</a></span>) Implemented condor_status -annex (w/o name) as an abbreviation of -annex-slots (so that -annex-name could deal with annex names starting with '-').  (By Todd L Miller )</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>", "type": "enhance", "last_change": "2017-Aug-16 19:28", "status": "resolved", "created": "2017-Jun-22 09:14", "fixed_version": "2017-Jun-22 09:14", "broken_version": "", "priority": "2", "subsystem": "Annex", "assigned_to": "tlmiller", "derived_from": "#6111", "creator": "tlmiller", "rust": "", "customer_group": "other", "visibility": "public", "notify": "tlmiller@cs.wisc.edu", "due_date": ""}